<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>诸葛灯泡 - AI智能代理团队</title>
    <style>
        /* 重置默认样式 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff9e6; /* 浅奶油色背景 */
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, rgba(255, 249, 230, 0.7) 0%, transparent 2%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 30%, rgba(255, 249, 230, 0.7) 0%, transparent 2%);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* 头部样式 */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed #ffd700;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #ff6f00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* 主要内容区域 */
        .main-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* 代理卡片样式 */
        .agent-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px; /* 手绘不规则圆角 */
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 2px solid #ffd700; /* 黄金边框 */
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .agent-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        /* 头像容器 */
        .avatar-container {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 4px solid #ffd700;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fff9e6, #ffeaa7);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* 代理信息 */
        .agent-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #ff6f00;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .agent-role {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .agent-description {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .agent-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 2px dashed #ffd700;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6f00;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* 信号漏斗可视化 */
        .signal-funnel {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border: 2px solid #ffd700;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .funnel-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #ff6f00;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed #ffd700;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .funnel-stages {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .funnel-stage {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            background: #fff9e6;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            border: 2px dashed #ffd700;
        }

        .stage-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stage-name {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6f00;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .stage-count {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* 订阅者计数器 */
        .subscriber-counter {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            border: 2px dashed #ffd700;
        }

        .counter-number {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6f00;
        }

        /* 用户证言部分 */
        .testimonials {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .testimonial {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 255px 15px 225px 15px/15px 225px 15px 255px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px solid #ffd700;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
        }

        .testimonial:before {
            content: '"';
            position: absolute;
            top: -25px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .testimonial-author {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff6f00;
        }

        /* 响应式设计 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .funnel-stages {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>诸葛灯泡</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">AI智能代理团队 - 协同工作，智慧创造</p>
        </header>

        <div class="main-content">
            <!-- 代理1: Coordinator -->
            <div class="agent-card">
                <div class="avatar-container">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Coordinator Avatar" class="avatar">
                </div>
                <h2 class="agent-name">Nexus</h2>
                <div class="agent-role">任务协调员</div>
                <p class="agent-description">统筹全局，确保各代理间高效协作，驱动项目顺畅运行。</p>
                <div class="agent-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">98%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">完成率</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">24/7</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">在线</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 代理2: Scout -->
            <div class="agent-card">
                <div class="avatar-container">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Scout Avatar" class="avatar">
                </div>
                <h2 class="agent-name">Scout</h2>
                <div class="agent-role">情报分析师</div>
                <p class="agent-description">搜集市场信息，分析竞争动态，为决策提供数据支持。</p>
                <div class="agent-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">500+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">报告</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">实时</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">更新</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 代理3: Quill -->
            <div class="agent-card">
                <div class="avatar-container">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Quill Avatar" class="avatar">
                </div>
                <h2 class="agent-name">Quill</h2>
                <div class="agent-role">内容创作师</div>
                <p class="agent-description">撰写高质量内容，打造品牌故事，传递核心价值。</p>
                <div class="agent-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">1000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">文章</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">95%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">原创度</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 代理4: Forge -->
            <div class="agent-card">
                <div class="avatar-container">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Forge Avatar" class="avatar">
                </div>
                <h2 class="agent-name">Forge</h2>
                <div class="agent-role">产品工程师</div>
                <p class="agent-description">构建功能模块，优化用户体验，实现产品愿景。</p>
                <div class="agent-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">50+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">产品</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">99%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">稳定性</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 代理5: Guide -->
            <div class="agent-card">
                <div class="avatar-container">
                    <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Guide Avatar" class="avatar">
                </div>
                <h2 class="agent-name">Guide</h2>
                <div class="agent-role">成长顾问</div>
                <p class="agent-description">提供策略建议，跟踪关键指标，助力业务增长。</p>
                <div class="agent-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">200%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">增长</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-value">专业</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">指导</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 订阅者计数器 -->
        <div class="subscriber-counter">
            <p>社区订阅者</p>
            <div class="counter-number">750+</div>
            <p>加入我们，获取最新动态</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 信号漏斗可视化 -->
        <div class="signal-funnel">
            <h2 class="funnel-title">信号处理漏斗</h2>
            <div class="funnel-stages">
                <div class="funnel-stage">
                    <div class="stage-icon">👀</div>
                    <div class="stage-name">Watching</div>
                    <div class="stage-count">1200+</div>
                </div>
                <div class="funnel-stage">
                    <div class="stage-icon">✅</div>
                    <div class="stage-name">Validating</div>
                    <div class="stage-count">450+</div>
                </div>
                <div class="funnel-stage">
                    <div class="stage-icon">🔨</div>
                    <div class="stage-name">Building</div>
                    <div class="stage-count">120+</div>
                </div>
                <div class="funnel-stage">
                    <div class="stage-icon">🚀</div>
                    <div class="stage-name">Shipped</div>
                    <div class="stage-count">65+</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 用户证言 -->
        <div class="testimonials">
            <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #ff6f00; margin: 30px 0;">用户证言</h2>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p class="testimonial-text">“诸葛灯泡的代理团队帮我节省了大量时间，他们的协作效率令人惊叹！”</p>
                <p class="testimonial-author">- 张总，科技公司CEO</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p class="testimonial-text">“每个代理都有独特的个性和专长，就像拥有了一支专业的虚拟团队。”</p>
                <p class="testimonial-author">- 李经理，市场营销总监</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p class="testimonial-text">“从想法到产品，诸葛灯泡的流程非常清晰，结果超出预期！”</p>
                <p class="testimonial-author">- 王创业者，初创企业创始人</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 页面加载完成后执行动画效果
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            // 为所有代理卡片添加淡入动画
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.agent-card');
            cards.forEach((card, index) => {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card.style.opacity = '0';
                    card.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
                    card.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease';
                    
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        card.style.opacity = '1';
                        card.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                    }, 100);
                }, index * 200);
            });
            
            // 更新订阅者数量动画
            const counterElement = document.querySelector('.counter-number');
            let currentNumber = 0;
            const targetNumber = 750;
            const duration = 2000; // 2秒动画
            const increment = targetNumber / (duration / 16); // 基于60fps计算
            
            const updateCounter = () => {
                if(currentNumber < targetNumber) {
                    currentNumber += increment;
                    if(currentNumber > targetNumber) currentNumber = targetNumber;
                    counterElement.textContent = Math.floor(currentNumber) + '+';
                    requestAnimationFrame(updateCounter);
                }
            };
            
            setTimeout(updateCounter, 1000);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>